                                         < The Game>
/* You are playing a game with your friend. The game involves n similar coins stacked on the top of each other. 
Each move of the game requires the top coin to be removed.
After each move, the number of coins n get reduced by 1. 
The person to remove the last coin wins. The game always begins with your friend getting the first move.
Return True if you win, else return False. */

class Solution 
{
public static String theGame(int n) 
{
if (n%2==0)
{
return "True";
}
else
{
return "False";
}
}
